<strong>HOPOS: The Journal of the International Society for the History of Philosophy of Science</strong>
</p>
<p>
The editors of HOPOS invite manuscript submissions for its 2011 inaugural issue.
The history of philosophy of science is broadly construed to include topics in
the history of related disciplines, in all time periods and all geographical
areas, using diverse methodologies. The journal does not limit submissions to
members of HOPOS.
</p>
